1. Videla sam helikopter kako leti preko zgrade. (*helikopter*) (I saw a helicopter flying over the building.)
2. Kupili smo novi model helikoptera za našu kolekciju. (*helikoptera*) (We bought a new model of a helicopter for our collection.)
3. Helikopterom su prevezli ranjenike u bolnicu. (*helikopterom*) (They transported the wounded to the hospital by helicopter.)
4. On je pilot helikoptera već pet godina. (*helikoptera*) (He has been a helicopter pilot for five years already.)
5. Moramo prevesti materijal helikopterom jer nema puta do tamo. (*helikopterom*) (We have to transport the material by helicopter because there is no road there.)
6. Helikopteri su postali nezamenljivi u spašavanju ljudi. (*helikopteri*) (Helicopters have become indispensable in rescuing people.)
7. Veliki helikopter sleteo je na pistu u vojnoj bazi. (*helikopter*) (A large helicopter landed on the runway at the military base.)
8. Helikopterima su se prevozili posetioci sa jednog ostrva na drugo. (*helikopterima*) (Visitors were transported by helicopters from one island to another.)
9. Helikopter koji smo videli je bio vojni. (*helikopter*) (The helicopter we saw was military.)
10. Za snimanje ovog filma upotrebljen je najnoviji model helikoptera. (*helikoptera*) (The latest model of a helicopter was used for filming this movie.)